  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/tabletpcs/\" rel=\"tag\">平板电脑</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/www.engadget.com/media/2013/10/apple-live-0653-1382466334.jpg\" /></div>\n\n<div><br />\n有新设计的 iPad air 和稍为加厚的 iPad mini with Retina display，当然也要有新的保护套啰，所以在发布会尾段，Apple 也发表了官方的专用机套，包括售 US$39（约人民币 240 元），和现有相似的标准翻盖式保护套、以及售 US$79（约人民币 480 元）的皮革版本；当然还有标志性的 Product Red 保护套，虽然价格还没公布，但想必是比较贵的吧？<br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/ipad-air-ipad-mini-with-retina-display/\">iPad Air / iPad mini with Retina display 保護套</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/ipad-air-ipad-mini-with-retina-display/6258876/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/022apple-live-0653-1-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/ipad-air-ipad-mini-with-retina-display/6258877/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/022apple-live-0655-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/ipad-air-ipad-mini-with-retina-display/6258879/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/10/022apple-live-0656-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a></div><br />\n<br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/10/22/apple-announces-new-covers-for-the-ipad-air-and-ipad-mini-price/\">Engadget</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/22/apple-announces-new-covers-for-the-ipad-air-and-ipad-mini-price/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20751703/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/22/apple-announces-new-covers-for-the-ipad-air-and-